Mixed-License Repository

This repository is an aggregation of first-party quadruped navigation code and
third-party ROS packages. Unless a file, directory, or package declares a
different license, first-party code in this extracted navigation workspace is
licensed under the Apache License 2.0. A copy of the Apache License 2.0 is
provided in LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt.

Third-party packages keep their original licenses. In particular:

- src/FAST_LIO is distributed under GPL-2.0-only according to its LICENSE file.
- src/livox_ros_driver2 is distributed under the Livox/MIT license text in that package.
- AgiBot/ZsiBot SDK files are distributed under BSD-3-Clause according to their LICENSE file.
- unused_packages/LIO-SAM is distributed under BSD-3-Clause according to its LICENSE file.
- RoboSense and YESENSE optional packages in unused_packages keep their upstream licenses.

See NOTICE for the package-by-package attribution list. The license files inside
each third-party package are authoritative for that package.
